  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vypren\" title=\"House Vypren\"><img alt=\"House Vypren.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/50px-House_Vypren.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/75px-House_Vypren.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/100px-House_Vypren.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Vorian Vypren</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vypren\" title=\"House Vypren\"><img alt=\"House Vypren.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/50px-House_Vypren.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/75px-House_Vypren.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/100px-House_Vypren.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Vypren\" title=\"House Vypren\">House Vypren</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Vorian Vypren</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vypren\" title=\"House Vypren\">House Vypren</a> and a warlord of the <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vorian_Vypren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_Invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal Invasion\">Andal Invasion</a>, he was one of the many warlords that conquered the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a>. At the <a href=\"/index.php/Widow%27s_Ford\" title=\"Widow&#39;s Ford\">Widow's Ford</a>, Vypren and his <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> were held back by three sons of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">Darry</a> for a day and a night before being victorious.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vorian_Vypren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404103814\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.057 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.229 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 417/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10392/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4886/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 362/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 567/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  220.544      1 -total\n 97.34%  214.678      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.80%  213.494      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.71%   25.821     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.50%    7.728      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.98%    4.376      1 Template:Ref\n  1.19%    2.624      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.61%    1.344      1 Template:References\n  0.43%    0.943      2 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18867-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404103814 and revision id 301218\n -->\n",
